ir new chair and enjoy the comforts that regular massage can Read More Massage During Pregnancy.";i:55;s:69:"Many think of massage as a luxury to be indulged in only on occasion.";i:56;s:28:"Pregnancy and Chair Massage.";i:57;s:51:"Another consideration is if the client is pregnant.";i:58;s:98:"This may mean they can no longer tolerate certain positions such as laying prone or on their back.";i:59;s:45:"They may just prefer a chair massage as well.";i:60;s:98:"There is a special chair made for prenatal clients that can provide a more comfortable experience.";i:61;s:16:"If in a regular.";}}